Not too much salt!

12
00:01:41,400 --> 00:01:42,923
Don't forget the tape deck!

13
00:01:46,505 --> 00:01:49,023
(remote clicks)

14
00:01:49,023 --> 00:01:50,540
- Popcorn, just the way you like it.

15
00:01:50,540 --> 00:01:51,480
