right ones until Monday.

627
00:29:42,970 --> 00:29:47,180
And after I got yelled at for
that, Nell canceled lunch.

628
00:29:47,180 --> 00:29:48,173
- Who did?
- She was gonna turn me on to

629
00:29:48,173 --> 00:29:51,450
this great soul food restaurant
