00:29:51,450 --> 00:29:54,443
But she went to the doctor instead.

631
00:29:54,443 --> 00:29:55,276
- Huh.

632
00:29:55,276 --> 00:29:56,620
- David said it's a
miracle she went at all

633
00:29:56,620 --> 00:29:58,210
because she really is the opposite

634
00:29:58,210 --> 00:30:00,358
