636
00:30:01,590 --> 00:30:03,292
(Zoey chuckles)

637
00:30:03,292 --> 00:30:04,125
- You wanna go with us?

638
00:30:04,125 --> 00:30:05,940
- What, to the doctor?

639
00:30:05,940 --> 00:30:08,254
- No, to the soul food restaurant.

