654
00:30:58,134 --> 00:31:00,801
(Elisa humming)

655
00:31:08,357 --> 00:31:11,357
(tense piano music)

656
00:31:18,360 --> 00:31:19,880
- David, morning.

657
00:31:19,880 --> 00:31:20,993
- Morning, Sam.

658
00:31:23,254 --> 00:31:24,780
(clears throat) Where is she?

659
00:31:24,780 --> 00:31:25,800
- She's in jail.

660
00:31:25,800 --> 00:31:26,930
