662
00:31:29,606 --> 00:31:30,710
(chuckles) Anyway, they arrested her

663
00:31:30,710 --> 00:31:31,960
but she wouldn't let me pay bail.

664
00:31:31,960 --> 00:31:33,610
She wants to experience being a prisoner

