00:31:37,540 --> 00:31:39,660
- Well, she's been incarcerated before.

668
00:31:39,660 --> 00:31:42,700
Jaywalking conflict, picketing
an animal research lab.

669
00:31:42,700 --> 00:31:43,620
Of course, she'd say we're all

