jail are more honest.

672
00:31:48,767 --> 00:31:50,691
(David chuckles)

673
00:31:50,691 --> 00:31:52,240
- (sighs) All right, look,
I need the tower plans.

674
00:31:52,240 --> 00:31:53,340
- Nell's got 'em.

675
00:31:53,340 --> 00:31:54,923
