676
00:31:56,700 --> 00:31:58,840
(Sam groans)

677
00:31:58,840 --> 00:32:00,478
- I do appreciate your generosity,

678
00:32:00,478 --> 00:32:02,160
but I simply told David I did
not want to be bailed out!

679
00:32:02,160 --> 00:32:04,350
- Believe me, the last thing I wanted

680
00:32:04,350 --> 00:32:05,927
to do was to bail you out, okay?

681
00:32:05,927 --> 00:32:07,820
But the tower plans happened to be locked

682
00:32:07,820 --> 00:32:10,112
