open unless you are there.

683
00:32:10,112 --> 00:32:10,945
(siren wails)
- Okay, fine.

684
00:32:10,945 --> 00:32:12,120
They can open the car,
you can have your plans,

685
00:32:12,120 --> 00:32:12,953
I'm going for a burger.

686
00:32:12,953 --> 00:32:14,227
- Yeah, well you're gonna have to walk.

