(Zoey sighs)

702
00:33:42,230 --> 00:33:44,800
- Look, it's not like I'm
(stammers) joining a cult

703
00:33:44,800 --> 00:33:46,410
or getting tattooed, I--

704
00:33:46,410 --> 00:33:47,910
- I'd rather you get tattooed.

705
00:33:48,840 --> 00:33:51,330
- Lots of people go back to school

706
00:33:51,330 --> 00:33:53,590
and graduate, and pursue careers!

707
00:33:53,590 --> 00:33:55,548
- But honey, you have two years to go.

708
00:33:55,548 --> 00:33:56,381
(Zoey sighs)

709
00:33:56,381 --> 00:33:58,440
I mean, doesn't Zack want you to graduate?

710
00:33:58,440 --> 00:33:59,550
He did!

711
00:33:59,550 --> 00:34:02,270
